Recruiters distribute tote bags filled with branded notebooks and pens while reminding students to follow up with personalized emails. A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. After the event, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly, while volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures.

Consulting firms stack glossy case study booklets on high tables for attendees, and a whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews. Meanwhile, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails.
